objenome.solver.evolve.init

Interface TypedInitialization

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OrganismBuilder<TypedOrganism>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Full, Grow, RampedHalfAndHalf

    public interface TypedInitialization
extends OrganismBuilder<TypedOrganism>
    Initialisation method for STGPIndividuals. It does not define any methods, but initialisation procedures that generate STGPIndividual objects should implement this interface.

    Where appropriate, implementations should use the MAXIMUM_INITIAL_DEPTH configuration parameter defined in this interface to specify the maximum depth of the program trees they generate. The TypedOrganism.MAXIMUM_DEPTH parameter should also be enforced.

    Since:
    2.0
